Rule: (L1) Ensure 'Windows Firewall: Public: Logging: Log dropped packets' is set to 'Yes'
Standard: CIS Microsoft Windows 10 Enterprise Release 21H1 Benchmark

Rule: (L1) Ensure 'Always prompt for password upon connection' is set to 'Enabled'
Standard: CIS Microsoft Windows 10 Enterprise Release 21H1 Benchmark

Rule: (L1) Ensure 'Internet Connection Sharing (ICS) (SharedAccess)' is set to 'Disabled'
Standard: CIS Microsoft Windows 10 Enterprise Release 21H1 Benchmark

Rule: (L1) Ensure 'Configure registry policy processing: Process even if the Group Policy objects have not changed' is set to 'Enabled: TRUE'
Standard: CIS Microsoft Windows 10 Enterprise Release 21H1 Benchmark

Rule: (L1) Ensure 'Password Settings: Password Complexity' is set to 'Enabled: Large letters + small letters + numbers + special characters'
Standard: CIS Microsoft Windows 10 Enterprise Release 21H1 Benchmark

Rule: (L1) Ensure 'Allow unencrypted traffic' is set to 'Disabled'
Standard: CIS Microsoft Windows 10 Enterprise Release 21H1 Benchmark

Rule: (L1) Ensure 'Audit Security Group Management' is set to include 'Success'
Standard: CIS Microsoft Windows 10 Enterprise Release 21H1 Benchmark

Rule: (L1) Ensure 'Prevent downloading of enclosures' is set to 'Enabled'
Standard: CIS Microsoft Windows 10 Enterprise Release 21H1 Benchmark

Rule: (L1) Ensure 'Turn off shell protocol protected mode' is set to 'Disabled'
Standard: CIS Microsoft Windows 10 Enterprise Release 21H1 Benchmark

Rule: (L1) Ensure 'Configure Automatic Updates: Scheduled install day' is set to '0 - Every day'
Standard: CIS Microsoft Windows 10 Enterprise Release 21H1 Benchmark
